License: MIT
Requirements: Growl, GrowlNotify

Triggeres Growl system notification on Mac systems

This implementation uses growlnotify found in the extras in the Growl package.
Default installer should put all files into /usr/local/bin/, don't forget to change this if growlnotify is somewhere else.

Download Growl from http://growl.info/
